Show Stored Document

Call the `{{tool_prefix}}category_list_files` tool:

```
{{tool_prefix}}category_list_files(
    category="{{args.0.value}}",
    source="stored",
    name="{{args.1.value}}"
)
```

After the tool call completes, inspect the result:
- If the result is empty, tell the user the stored document was not found
- Otherwise display the full document detail including:
  - Category and name
  - Source and source type
  - Created and updated timestamps
  - All metadata entries
